{
  "page": "Edric Dayne",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\"><img alt=\"House Dayne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/50px-House_Dayne.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/75px-House_Dayne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/100px-House_Dayne.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Edric Dayne</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\"><img alt=\"Brotherhood without banners.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/50px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/75px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/7/7b/Brotherhood_without_banners.svg/100px-Brotherhood_without_banners.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Edric_dayne_by_eluas.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Edric dayne by eluas.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/39/Edric_dayne_by_eluas.jpg/350px-Edric_dayne_by_eluas.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"569\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/39/Edric_dayne_by_eluas.jpg/525px-Edric_dayne_by_eluas.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/39/Edric_dayne_by_eluas.jpg/700px-Edric_dayne_by_eluas.jpg 2x\" /></a><div>Edric Dayne, by eluas ©</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Alias</th><td>\nNed<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Title</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Starfall\" title=\"Lord of Starfall\">Lord of Starfall</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiances</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">brotherhood without banners</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Stony Dornishmen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Years_after_Aegon%27s_Conquest#Year_287_After_the_Conquest\" title=\"Years after Aegon&#39;s Conquest\">287&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Starfall\" title=\"Starfall\">Starfall</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafedric_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafedric_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Dayne_(father_of_Edric)\" title=\"Lord Dayne (father of Edric)\">Lord Dayne</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appendix)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Edric Dayne</b>, also known as <b>Ned</b>, is the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Starfall\" title=\"Lord of Starfall\">Lord of Starfall</a> and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a>. His <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Dayne_(father_of_Edric)\" title=\"Lord Dayne (father of Edric)\">father</a>, whose name is unknown, was the elder brother of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur</a>, Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Ashara_Dayne\" title=\"Ashara Dayne\">Ashara</a>, and Lady <a href=\"/index.php/Allyria_Dayne\" title=\"Allyria Dayne\">Allyria Dayne</a>. Edric serves as the <a href=\"/index.php/Squire\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Squire\">squire</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Blackhaven\" title=\"Lord of Blackhaven\">Lord of Blackhaven</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#History\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">History</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Game_of_Thrones\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#A_Feast_for_Crows\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Quotes_by_Edric\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes by Edric</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Quotes_about_Edric\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes about Edric</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Family\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Family</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">See also: <a href=\"/index.php/Category:Images_of_Edric_Dayne\" title=\"Category:Images of Edric Dayne\">Images of Edric Dayne</a></div>\n<p>At the time of <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, Edric is twelve years old.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasosappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> His fair hair<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is pale blond,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> and his dark blue eyes appear almost <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_eyes\" title=\"Purple eyes\">purple</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> Lord Dayne wears a pale purple cloak.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Although he can be shy, Edric is good-natured and polite.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:352px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Edric_Dayne_Dimitri_Bielak.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/62/Edric_Dayne_Dimitri_Bielak.jpg/350px-Edric_Dayne_Dimitri_Bielak.jpg\" width=\"350\" height=\"350\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/62/Edric_Dayne_Dimitri_Bielak.jpg/525px-Edric_Dayne_Dimitri_Bielak.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/62/Edric_Dayne_Dimitri_Bielak.jpg/700px-Edric_Dayne_Dimitri_Bielak.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Edric_Dayne_Dimitri_Bielak.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Edric by Dimitri Bielak © Fantasy Flight Games</div></div></div>\n<p>Edric was born at <a href=\"/index.php/Starfall\" title=\"Starfall\">Starfall</a>, in <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a>, to <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Dayne_(father_of_Edric)\" title=\"Lord Dayne (father of Edric)\">Lord Dayne</a> and his wife. Edric's mother did not have enough milk for him when he was born, so he was <a href=\"/index.php/Wet_nurse\" title=\"Wet nurse\">nursed</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Wylla\" title=\"Wylla\">Wylla</a>, a servant at Starfall.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> At some point, Edric was told that Wylla was the mother of <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Bastard\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Bastard\">bastard</a> of Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>When Edric was seven, his aunt <a href=\"/index.php/Allyria_Dayne\" title=\"Allyria Dayne\">Allyria</a> was betrothed to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a>, and Edric went to <a href=\"/index.php/Blackhaven\" title=\"Blackhaven\">Blackhaven</a> with Beric to serve as his page. Beric raised Edric to squire when he turned ten. He once won a prize <a href=\"/index.php/Riding_at_rings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Riding at rings\">riding at rings</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Edric has never killed anyone.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Game_of_Thrones\"><i>A Game of Thrones</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Game of Thrones\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Edric attends the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand%27s_tourney\" title=\"Hand&#39;s tourney\">Hand's tourney</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> and sees Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a>, the new <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">Hand of the King</a> to <a href=\"/index.php/Robert_I_Baratheon\" title=\"Robert I Baratheon\">Robert I Baratheon</a>. Young Edric wants to go and speak with Eddard, but he does not know what to say. He also sees <a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a> at the tourney, when Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Loras_Tyrell\" title=\"Loras Tyrell\">Loras Tyrell</a> gives her a rose.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-10\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>As Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric Dondarrion</a>'s squire, Edric is part of the force sent by Lord Eddard to the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a> to apprehend Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gregor_Clegane\" title=\"Gregor Clegane\">Gregor Clegane</a> for raiding the <a href=\"/index.php/Riverlands\" title=\"Riverlands\">riverlands</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> After the force is ambushed in the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_Mummer%27s_Ford\" title=\"Battle at the Mummer&#39;s Ford\">battle at the Mummer's Ford</a>, Edric pulls the dying Beric out of the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a> and stands over the body while the battle rages around them.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-11\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Edric continues to squire for the revived Lord Beric, whose outlaws fight to protect <a href=\"/index.php/Smallfolk\" title=\"Smallfolk\">smallfolk</a> in the riverlands during the <a href=\"/index.php/War_of_the_Five_Kings\" title=\"War of the Five Kings\">War of the Five Kings</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok26.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>When <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> is taken by the <a href=\"/index.php/Brotherhood_without_banners\" title=\"Brotherhood without banners\">brotherhood without banners</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Hollow_hill\" title=\"Hollow hill\">hollow hill</a>, she sees that Lord Beric has a young squire named Ned, who helps remove his breastplate. She is unnerved by hearing the name \"Ned\", the same nickname as her father Eddard's. Ned brings Beric his sword, surcoat, and shield before Beric fights a duel with <a href=\"/index.php/Sandor_Clegane\" title=\"Sandor Clegane\">Sandor Clegane</a>. After Beric is killed in the duel, <a href=\"/index.php/Thoros_of_Myr\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Thoros of Myr\">Thoros of Myr</a> has Ned help him with Beric's body before the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_priest\" title=\"Red priest\">red priest</a> revives the lightning lord with the <a href=\"/index.php/Last_kiss\" title=\"Last kiss\">last kiss</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Ned fights alongside Beric during the <a href=\"/index.php/Battle_at_the_burning_septry\" title=\"Battle at the burning septry\">battle at the burning septry</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_8-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos39.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup> and he accompanies the outlaws to <a href=\"/index.php/High_Heart\" title=\"High Heart\">High Heart</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> It rains through the night at High Heart, and Ned wakes up with chills.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Edric attempts to befriend a wary Arya during the brotherhood's travels, and her friend <a href=\"/index.php/Gendry\" title=\"Gendry\">Gendry</a> is scornful of their interactions. Ned tells Arya that he saw her father Eddard and sister Sansa at the Hand's tourney. Ned states that he and Arya's half-brother <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> are <a href=\"/index.php/Milk_brother\" title=\"Milk brother\">milk brothers</a>; that is, his <a href=\"/index.php/Wet_nurse\" title=\"Wet nurse\">wet nurse</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Wylla\" title=\"Wylla\">Wylla</a>, who has been a servant of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">House Dayne</a> for many years, is Jon's mother, and swears that this is true on the honor of his house.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-14\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> When Arya asks who he is, Ned reveals he is the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Starfall\" title=\"Lord of Starfall\">Lord of Starfall</a>. Ned tells Arya more about his family, and he is surprised that her father never spoke of Edric's aunt <a href=\"/index.php/Ashara_Dayne\" title=\"Ashara Dayne\">Ashara</a> committing suicide over her broken heart. Ned hesitantly tells Arya that his aunt <a href=\"/index.php/Allyria_Dayne\" title=\"Allyria Dayne\">Allyria</a> told him that Ashara and Eddard fell in love at the <a href=\"/index.php/Tourney_at_Harrenhal\" title=\"Tourney at Harrenhal\">tourney at Harrenhal</a>. Arya is upset to hear that her father might have loved someone besides her mother <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">Catelyn</a>. Edric tries to apologize, but she does not want to hear it and rides away from him.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-15\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Feast_for_Crows\"><i>A Feast for Crows</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Feast for Crows\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>After Beric's final death,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_9-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc42.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup> Edric and several other members of Beric's band<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_10-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-10\">&#91;10&#93;</a></sup> go their separate ways from those who choose to follow the resurrected, vengeful <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Stoneheart\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Lady Stoneheart\">Lady Stoneheart</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafedric_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafedric_dayne.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_by_Edric\">Quotes by Edric</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes by Edric\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Edric_Dayne_by_Gaya-the-K.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/27/Edric_Dayne_by_Gaya-the-K.jpg/250px-Edric_Dayne_by_Gaya-the-K.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"585\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/27/Edric_Dayne_by_Gaya-the-K.jpg/375px-Edric_Dayne_by_Gaya-the-K.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/2/27/Edric_Dayne_by_Gaya-the-K.jpg/500px-Edric_Dayne_by_Gaya-the-K.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Edric_Dayne_by_Gaya-the-K.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Edric by Gaya-the-K ©</div></div></div>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Edric</b>: I won a prize once, <a href=\"/index.php/Riding_at_rings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Riding at rings\">riding at rings</a>.<br />\n</p><p><b>Arya</b>: I never learned the lance, but I could beat you with a sword. Have you killed anyone?<br />\n</p>\n<b>Edric</b>: I'm only twelve.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-16\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Edric and <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Arya</b>: You have a House? Who are you?<br />\n<b>Edric</b>: My lady? I'm Edric Dayne, the ... the <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Starfall\" title=\"Lord of Starfall\">Lord of Starfall</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-17\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a> and Edric</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Quotes_about_Edric\">Quotes about Edric</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Quotes about Edric\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>Arya got goosebumps when Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Beric_Dondarrion\" title=\"Beric Dondarrion\">Beric</a> said <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">her father's</a> name, but this Ned was only a boy, a fair-haired squire no more than ten or twelve.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The squire seemed nice enough to Arya; maybe a little shy, but good-natured. She had always heard that <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a> were small and swarthy, with black hair and small black eyes, but Ned had big blue eyes, so dark that they looked almost <a href=\"/index.php/Purple_eyes\" title=\"Purple eyes\">purple</a>. And his hair was a pale blond, more ash than honey.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-18\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;thoughts of <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Arya</b>: <a href=\"/index.php/Dornishmen\" title=\"Dornishmen\">Dornishmen</a> lie, don't they?<br />\n</p><p><b>Anguy</b>: They're famous for it. Of course, they say the same of us <a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">marchers</a>, so there you are. What's the trouble now? Ned's a good lad ...<br />\n</p>\n<b>Arya</b>: He's just a stupid liar.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-19\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos43.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Anguy\" title=\"Anguy\">Anguy</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Edric_Dayne&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif\">&#160;</span></div></td><td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black\"><div style=\"width:1em; height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div></td><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black;\"><div style=\"width:2em;height:1em;\"><span style=\"font:1px/1px serif;\">&#160;</span></div